wiki.content:
So its Peter Tosh and another very well known singer?
 Heading one of the biggest bands in the world?
 Not known for his reggae, Mick Jagger recorded this single when on a trip to Jamaica.
 Following on from the recording there is an iconic photo of the two sitting in the gutter enjoying a smoke.
 The track is about being positive, looking forward and having no regrets.
